<h2 style="color: #333333; margin-bottom: 20px;">Verify Your Email Address</h2>

<p>Hi <%= userName %>,</p>

<p>Welcome to <%= fromName %>! We're excited to have you on board. To get started, please verify your email address by clicking the button below.</p>

<div style="background-color: #f8f8f8; padding: 25px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 30px 0; text-align: center;">
  <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Please click the button below to verify your email:</p>
  <a href="<%= verificationUrl %>" class="button">Verify Email</a>
  <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #666666;">
    This link will expire in <%= expirationTime %>
  </p>
</div>

<div style="margin: 30px 0;">
  <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 14px;">Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
  <p style="word-break: break-all; background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px;">
    <%= verificationUrl %>
  </p>
</div>

<div style="background-color: #e0f2fe; border: 1px solid #7dd3fc; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 30px 0;">
  <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #0369a1;">âœ¨ What happens next?</h4>
  <ul style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #0369a1;">
    <li style="margin-bottom: 5px;">Your email will be verified</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 5px;">You'll receive a welcome email with helpful tips</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 5px;">You can start shopping and enjoying our services</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #666666;">
  If you didn't create an account with <%= fromName %>, please ignore this email. 
  No account will be created without verifying this email address.
</p>

<p style="margin-top: 20px; color: #666666;">
  For security reasons, this verification link will expire in <%= expirationTime %>. 
  If it expires, you can request a new verification link from your account settings.
</p>

<div style="margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
  <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 14px;">
    Need help? Contact our support team at 
    <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>" style="color: #3b82f6;"><%= supportEmail %></a>
  </p>
</div>